videos.description: Keldon Johnson steps in front of a lazy pass, then goes the other way for the thunderous two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson fires up Big Blue Nation with an early steal and slam) 2019/01/22

videos.headline: Johnson fires up Big Blue Nation with an early steal and slam

videos.description: Right after Keldon Johnson misses a fastbreak jam, PJ Washington frustrates John Calipari with a miss of his own.
videos.headline: Kentucky misses back-to-back dunks

videos.description: Reid Travis steps in for the steal, then Ashton Hagans makes the nice feed to PJ Washington for the transition flush.

videos.description: Abdul Ado has a big denial for Mississippi State on defense, then Quinndary Weatherspoon goes the other way for the Eurostep lay-in.

videos.headline: Ado's block leads to Q. Weatherspoon's Euro layup for Bulldogs

videos.description: Tyler Herro sees his big man open down low, so he fires a pass to Nick Richards for the easy flush.
